{"type": "article", "id": 2317, "title": "Adidas Tech Super 跑鞋", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-11T21:35:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222217jvLqQK8Y7EG3mNM6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t1992 年的巴塞罗那奥运会上，阿迪达斯曾推出一款经典跑鞋 Tech Super 。日前，设计团队为 Tech Super 打造了全新的配色 Collegiate Navy &amp; Night Cargo ，延续其复古的轮廓，鞋身采用麂皮与网眼结合制作，配色上则将橄榄绿、深蓝色和黄色组合制造对比感，同时再搭载白色中底呈现。定价 89 英镑，<a href=\"http://www.endclothing.co.uk/latest-products/adidas-tech-super-218497.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222216Xmq42LSkCtsriuvP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222216gvKXQ0bT9CFNRruk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222217ntcodL63lbsaDNMq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}